      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_02-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "振り付けも、完璧に揃ってる。この人ら\nVENUSプログラムでの点数のとり方を知ってるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Their choreography is perfectly in sync as well.\nThese girls know how to score points in the VENUS Program.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.733333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_02-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "ダンスは私が今まで見たどのアイドルよりも\nうまく見える",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Their dancing looks way better than any other idol group\nI’ve seen before.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.833333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon",
      "startTime": 23.433333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_02-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "間違いなく、今の私達よりも上ね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They’re definitely better than us right now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.433333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon",
      "startTime": 27.266666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_02-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "ダンスだけでも、トップクラスゆうことか～\nどんだけ才能あんの、この人達……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Their dancing alone is top class!\nThese girls are choke-full of talent…",
        "id": ""
