      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_02-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "……まぁ、あのパフォーマンスなら\n勝って当然、というべきやなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ with that performance‚\nthey totally deserved to win.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
