      "text": "あれだけ激しく踊ってたのに……\nまだ余裕ある感じだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "despite their energetic dancing…\nIt’s like it was a walk in the park for them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.23333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
