      "text": "……これがスリクス\nBIG4の一角の実力なのね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…So‚ this is what IIIX‚\none of the pillars of the BIG4‚ is capable of…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.766666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
