      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon",
      "startTime": 56.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_02-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "うちら、この子達と戦うんか……\nあかん、うち、ちょっと緊張してきた……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’re competing against these girls?\nOh boy‚ I’m getting a little nervous.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.833333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_02-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "で、でも、勝負は実力だけで\n決まる訳じゃないよ！　と、時の運とか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "B-but battles aren’t won\non abilities alone! Th-there’s luck involved as well…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tri-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 71.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_02-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "……そうやね。グランプリの時だって\n実力で劣る月ストやサニピが勝ち上がった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "True. During the Grand Prix‚ Moon Tempest\nand Sunny Peace lacked abilities‚ but they won.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.66666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon",
