      "text": "今のうちらの調子は、これ以上ないほどにいい\n……化学反応を起こせれば、勝てない相手ちゃう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’re in better shape than we’ve ever been before.\nIf we can cause another chemical reaction‚ we can beat them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon",
