      "text": "今のパフォーマンスを観て\nどうしても確かめたくなったの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Seeing that performance just now\nmade me want to confirm something.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat-00-noon",
      "startTime": 105.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_10_02-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "確かめるって……誰に、何を？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Confirm something? With who and what?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
