      "text": "私達がアイドルの頂点に立つために、邪魔な存在は\n排除します。たとえ同じ事務所の貴方達でも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’ll eliminate any obstacles that stand in our way to the top‚\nwhether it be idols from our own agency.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 319.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
